articles.title: DRAMATIC VIDEO: Man flung from aircraft onto tailplane in dramatic skydiving mishap - ABC7 Los Angeles
articles.description: Dramatic video shows a skydiver's reserve parachute becoming snagged on a plane wing mid-air over Queensland, Australia.
articles.content:
QUEENSLAND, Australia -- Dramatic video from Australia shows a skydiver's reserve parachute becoming snagged on a plane wing mid-air over Queensland.
The video was released on Thursday, December 11 … [+1100 chars]
